@startuml
title Embedded Resource 및 다중 요청 상황 처리 기준

actor User as U
participant "Browser/JMeter" as B
participant "Static Resource\nJS/CSS/Image/Font" as STATIC
participant "Protected API" as API
participant "Frontend\nInterceptor" as FE
participant "Auth API\n/refresh" as AUTH

U -> B: 화면 진입

B -> STATIC: GET /static/app.js
STATIC --> B: 200 OK

B -> STATIC: GET /static/style.css
STATIC --> B: 200 OK

B -> STATIC: GET /images/logo.png
STATIC --> B: 200 OK

B -> FE: 화면 스크립트 실행

FE -> API: GET /api/menu\nexpiredAccessToken
FE -> API: GET /api/user\nexpiredAccessToken
FE -> API: GET /api/permission\nexpiredAccessToken
FE -> API: GET /api/dashboard\nexpiredAccessToken

API --> FE: 401 /api/menu
FE -> FE: Refresh 시작

API --> FE: 401 /api/user
FE -> FE: failedQueue 등록

API --> FE: 401 /api/permission
FE -> FE: failedQueue 등록

API --> FE: 401 /api/dashboard
FE -> FE: failedQueue 등록

FE -> AUTH: POST /api/auth/refresh\nrefreshToken
AUTH --> FE: 200 OK\nnewAccessToken

FE -> API: /api/menu 재시도\nnewAccessToken
FE -> API: /api/user 재시도\nnewAccessToken
FE -> API: /api/permission 재시도\nnewAccessToken
FE -> API: /api/dashboard 재시도\nnewAccessToken

API --> FE: 200 OK
API --> FE: 200 OK
API --> FE: 200 OK
API --> FE: 200 OK

note over B,STATIC
정적 리소스는 가능하면
JWT 인증/Refresh 흐름과 분리한다.
end note

note over FE,AUTH
업무 API가 여러 개 실패해도
Refresh는 1회로 단일화한다.
end note

@enduml